OL,3,CChatham launches ambitious bid to be
OL,4,Cnamed UK's first-ever 'Town of Culture'
OL,6,FChatham is officially throwing its hat
OL,7,Finto the ring to become the UK's first-
OL,8,Fever Town of Culture, aiming to secure
OL,9,Fa #3 million windfall that could
OL,10,Ftransform the Medway town.
OL,12,FThe new competition, announced by
OL,13,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy, follows
OL,14,Fthe success of the 'City of Culture'
OL,15,Ftitle which has previously revitalized
OL,16,Fplaces like Hull and Coventry.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
