OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772041214
OL,3,CChatham launches ambitious bid to be
OL,4,Cnamed UK's first-ever 'Town of Culture'
OL,6,FNow, the government is shifting its
OL,7,Ffocus away from major metropolitan
OL,8,Fhubs to celebrate the "unique stories"
OL,9,Fof the nation's towns. For Chatham`a
OL,10,Ftown with a rich naval history and a
OL,11,Frapidly growing creative scene`the bid
OL,12,Frepresents a once-in-a-generation
OL,13,Fopportunity.
OL,15,FThe UK Town of Culture 2028 is a brand-
OL,16,Fnew initiative. Unlike previous
OL,17,Fcompetitions, it specifically targets
OL,18,Fsmall, medium, and large towns,
OL,19,Fensuring they don't have to compete
OL,20,Fagainst massive cities for funding.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
