OL,3,CChatham launches ambitious bid to be
OL,4,Cnamed UK's first-ever 'Town of Culture'
OL,6,FThe winning town will receive:
OL,8,FThe two runners-up will also receive
OL,9,F#250,000 each to deliver parts of
OL,10,Ftheir cultural vision.
OL,12,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy, said the
OL,13,Fmove is about ensuring quality art,
OL,14,Fmusic, and drama are accessible to
OL,15,Feveryone, regardless of where they
OL,16,Flive.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
