PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1772041214
OL,3,CChatham launches ambitious bid to be
OL,4,Cnamed UK's first-ever 'Town of Culture'
OL,6,F"Great culture is not confined to our
OL,7,Flargest metropolitan centres; it is
OL,8,Feverywhere, rooted in communities
OL,9,Facross the country," she said. "Every
OL,10,Ftown has its own story and unique
OL,11,Fcontribution. Our government believes
OL,12,Fit should be seen and valued."
OL,14,FFor Chatham, that story stretches from
OL,15,Fthe historic Royal Dockyard to the
OL,16,Fmodern-day artists' studios popping up
OL,17,Fin the town centre.
